<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

  <head>

  </head>

  <body>
    <form>
      <style>
        .container-fluid {
          background-color: white;

          padding: 50px;
        }

        .photo {
          display: flex;

        }

        .img {
          display: inline;

          width: 150px;

          /* border: solid; */
          border: 1px solid black;
          padding-top: 0px;
          padding-right: 30px;
          padding-bottom: 100px;
          padding-left: 30px;


        }

        .elements {
          padding: 0px;
          display: inline;
          border-bottom: 1px solid;
          border-bottom-color: black;


        }

        .field {

          color: black;
          padding-left: 00px;
          padding-right: 250px;

        }

        .new {

          color: black;
          padding-left: 00px;
          padding-right: 75%;
        }

        input[type=email] {
          border: 0px solid;
          height: 20px;
          width: 90%;
          padding-left: 10px;

        }

        .details {
          text-align: left;
          width: 300px;
          padding: 6px 10px;
          margin: 1px 0;
          border: none;
          border-bottom: 1px;
          border-bottom-style: dashed;
          /* border-color: black; */
          /* box-sizing: unset; */
        }


        h5,
        h4 {
          margin-top: 1px;
        }

        /* input[type=text] {
            text-align: center;
            width: 160px;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
          } */

        #RegNo {
          text-align: center;
          width: 160px;
          padding: 6px 10px;
          margin: 8px 0;
          box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        textarea {
          margin-top: 1px;
        }

        table {
          border-collapse: collapse;
          width: 70%;

        }

        th {
          height: 10px;
          text-align: center;
        }

        th,
        td {
          padding: 10px;
          text-align: center;
        }

        #selectionTable {
          border-collapse: collapse;
          width: 50%;
        }

        #selectionTable th {
          height: min-content;
          text-align: center;
        }

        #selectionTable td {
          padding: 2px;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .date_table {
          width: 100%;

        }

        .date_table td {
          text-align: justify;

        }

        .Signature_table {
          width: 100%;
        }
      </style>

      <div class="container-fluid">

        <div class="photo">
          <div>
            <img src="<%= imgUrl %> " alt="" style="width: 3.5cm;height: 4.5cm;">
          </div>
          <div style="width: 70%;">
            <p style="text-align: center;"><em>Faculty of Applied Sciences</em><br>
              <em>Wayamba University of Sri Lanka</em>
            </p>
            <h4 align="center">Course Registration Form</h4>
            <p style="text-align: center;"><em>Acadamic Year: <%= data.personal.academicYear %> (Level
                <%= data.personal.level %> )</em><br>
              B.Sc.(Joint Major) Degree Program</p>
          </div>
        </div>



        <div align="right">
          <div style="display: inline-block;">
            <label for="RegNo">Reg No:</label>
            <input type="text" id="RegNo" name="username" value="<%= data.personal.regNo %>">
          </div>
        </div>


        <div>
          <div style="display: inline-block;margin-bottom: 4px;">
            <label for="test">01. Name in Full(Mr./Ms.):-</label>
            <label class="details"><%= data.personal.name %> </label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="display: inline-block;margin-top: 8px;">
            <label for="Title">02. Contact No. for Immediate Correspondence:-</label>
            <label class="details"><%= data.personal.contact %> </label>
          </div>
        </div>



        <p>03. Select Three Subject Combinations in the order of preference by putting 1,2,3 in the relevant cages:-
        </p>
        <table border="1px" align="center" id="selectionTable">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Combination</th>
              <th>Major 1</th>
              <th>Major 2</th>
              <th>Selected Combination</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% comb=data.personal.degreeDetails.combination %>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 1A</td>
              <td>CMIS</td>
              <td>ELTN</td>
              <td><%= comb==='1A'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 1B</td>
              <td>CMIS</td>
              <td>MMST</td>
              <td><%= comb==='1B'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 1C</td>
              <td>CMIS</td>
              <td>IMGT</td>
              <td><%= comb==='1C'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 2A</td>
              <td>ELTN</td>
              <td>CMIS</td>
              <td><%= comb==='2A'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 2B</td>
              <td>ELTN</td>
              <td>MMST</td>
              <td><%= comb==='2B'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 2C</td>
              <td>ELTN</td>
              <td>IMGT</td>
              <td><%= comb==='2C'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 3A</td>
              <td>IMGT</td>
              <td>ELTN</td>
              <td><%= comb==='3A'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 3B</td>
              <td>IMGT</td>
              <td>MMST</td>
              <td><%= comb==='3B'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 3C</td>
              <td>IMGT</td>
              <td>CMIS</td>
              <td><%= comb==='3C'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 4A</td>
              <td>MMST</td>
              <td>CMIS</td>
              <td><%= comb==='4A'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 4B</td>
              <td>MMST</td>
              <td>ELTN</td>
              <td><%= comb==='4B'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>COMB 4C</td>
              <td>MMST</td>
              <td>IMGT</td>
              <td><%= comb==='4C'?'✓':' ' %></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        </br>
        <p>Indicate in the tables below, the Course Modules of the Degree Program of your first preference, for which
          you wish to register. </p>
        </br>
        <h4>SEMESTER I</h4>
        <table border="1px" align="center">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Module Code</th>
              <th>Title of the Compulsory Module</th>
              <th>No. of Credits</th>

            </tr>
          </thead>
          <% var sem1Mandatory=data.semester1.mandatory %>
          <% for( let i = 0; i < sem1Mandatory.length; i++ ) { %>
          <tr>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Mandatory[i].code %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Mandatory[i].name %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Mandatory[i].credit %></td>
          </tr>
          <% } %>

          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td colspan="2">Total No. of Credits =</td>

          </tr>
        </table>
        </br>
        </br>
        <table border="1px" align="center" style="page-break-after: always;">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Module Code</th>
              <th>Title of the Optional Module</th>
              <th>No. of Credits</th>
          </thead>
          </tr>
          <% var sem1Optional=data.semester1.optional %>
          <% for( let i = 0; i < sem1Optional.length; i++ ) { %>
          <tr>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Optional[i].code %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Optional[i].name %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem1Optional[i].credit %></td>
          </tr>
          <% } %>

          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td colspan="2">Total No. of Credits =</td>

          </tr>
        </table>
        </br>
        </br>
        <h4>SEMESTER II</h4>
        <table border="1px" align="center">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Module Code</th>
              <th>Title of the Compulsory Module</th>
              <th>No. of Credits</th>

            </tr>
          </thead>
          <% var sem2Mandatory=data.semester2.mandatory %>
          <% for( let i = 0; i < sem2Mandatory.length; i++ ) { %>
          <tr>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Mandatory[i].code %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Mandatory[i].name %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Mandatory[i].credit %></td>
          </tr>
          <% } %>

          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td colspan="2">Total No. of Credits =</td>

          </tr>
        </table>
        </br>
        <br>
        <table border="1px" align="center">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Module Code</th>
              <th>Title of the Optional Module</th>
              <th>No. of Credits</th>

            </tr>
          </thead>

          <% var sem2Optional=data.semester2.optional %>
          <% for( let i = 0; i < sem2Optional.length; i++ ) { %>
          <tr>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Optional[i].code %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Optional[i].name %></td>
            <td style="vertical-align:middle"><%= sem2Optional[i].credit %></td>
          </tr>
          <% } %>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td colspan="2">Total No. of Credits =</td>

          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td colspan="3">Total number of credits for the academic year =</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p>04. Registration Fee: Rs. 150</p>
        <table class="date_table">
          <tr>
            <td>Date of Payments:</td>
            <td>Receipt No:</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Date: ...........................</td>
            <td>.................................</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Signature of Applicant</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        </br>
        <hr>
        <p>I certify that the above student has selected the correct set of modules relevant to his/her combination at
          level 3 and that he/she will fulfill the minimum annual credit requirement in respect of the subject area(s)
          offered by my Department </p>
        </br>
        </br>
        <table class="Signature_table">
          <tr>
            <td>..................................................</td>
            <td>..................................................</td>
            <td>..................................................</td>
            <td>..................................................</td>

          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/CMIS</td>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/ELTN</td>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/IMGT</td>
            <td>Signature of the Head/Academic Advisor/MATH</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>
            <td>Date...........................................</td>

          </tr>
        </table>
        </br>
        <p>I certify that the above student has selected required minimum/maximum number of modules aggregating to the
          number of credits................. for Level 3</p>
        </br>
        <p>.........................................................</p>
        <p>Signature of the Student Counsellor</p>

      </div>
    </form>
  </body>

</html>